#: ../../network.rst:7 587673cb857f4a7aa64b324a503cbb88
msgid ""
"The ``Interfaces and devices`` page configures how the server is "
"connected to the local network (LAN) and/or other networks (i.e. "
"Internet)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../network.rst:10 8843429ceeea40acb908d924d55c68ce
msgid ""
"NethSecurity supports an unlimited number of network interfaces. Any "
"network managed by the system must follow these rules:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../network.rst:13 3315489e9e0d4213ab4752f9422c5f11
msgid ""
"networks must be logically separated: each network must have different "
"addresses"
msgstr ""

#: ../../network.rst:14 8a70e661a9dc4b3faf489410b88a70a7
msgid ""
"private networks, like LANs, must follow address's convention from "
":ref:`RFC1918 <RFC1918-section>` document"
msgstr ""

#: ../../network.rst:15 1d32c335b6b040ada1272e0802b36173
msgid ""
"networks should be physically separated using different switches or "
"logically separated using VLAN (Virtual Local Area Network)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../network.rst:17 67fd35176c294f35a5ae913e3a3fd172
msgid ""
"Every network interface has a specific zone which determines its "
"behavior. A basic network setup for a router typically includes a minimum"
" of two interfaces, namely LAN (Local Area Network) and WAN (Wide Area "
"Network):"
msgstr ""

#: ../../network.rst:20 0ed348fb6398492cb9906925ca9023da
msgid ""
"*lan*: local network, hosts on this network can access any other "
"configured network"
msgstr ""

#: ../../network.rst:21 3ef149d28ba64b79b82931dac560df7d
msgid ""
"*wan*: public network, hosts on this network can access only the server "
"itself"
msgstr ""

#: ../../network.rst:23 961eaf9e187c4a63a85d3c02b0118338
msgid ""
"All configured network interfaces are listed at the top of the page. Each"
" interface is displayed with its name and the assigned firewall zone. "
"This section offers an immediate overview of the current configurations, "
"allowing users to quickly see which networks are already set up and "
"associated with specific security zones."
msgstr ""

#: ../../network.rst:28 006c6ff507a6400db3c230d82104c8eb
