"In the bottom section of the page, available but unconfigured network "
"devices are listed. To configure a device, the user clicks on the "
":guilabel:`Configure` button corresponding to the desired device. The "
"newly created :ref:`VLAN devices <vlan-section>` are visible in this "
"section."
