msgid "PPPoE"
msgstr ""

#: ../../network.rst:115 e56b8a3e5c9040dcaedccb65dc457b0a
msgid ""
"PPPoE (Point-to-Point Protocol over Ethernet) connects the server to "
"Internet through a DSL modem. Users can setup a new PPPoE connection "
"using an unassigned Ethernet network interface or creating a new logical "
"interface."
msgstr ""

#: ../../network.rst:118 e45588781bbe4b8e81779eb79839520d
msgid ""
"Inside the network interface window, choose the wan zone then, select the"
" ``PPPoE`` protocol. Then fill all required fields like ``Username`` and "
"``Password``."
msgstr ""

